</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Metacomet-Monadnock Trail</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><dl>
<dd><i>This topic is about the footpath located in Massachusetts and New Hampshire. It should not be confused with the similarly named <a href="/wiki/Metacomet_Trail" title="Metacomet Trail">Metacomet Trail</a> of Connecticut.</i></dd>
</dl>
<table class="infobox" style="width:22em">
